Some schools will include classical, modern languages in their program, while others will opt for languages considered to be most important in the United Kingdom in 2020, such as Mandarin or Japanese.
Regardless of your child's interests, independent schools will always have a wide range of choices, as well as teaching staff that is professional in this area.
Scottish independent schools provide children with an environment in which learners will prepare and arm the skills needed for success, regardless of what the future holds for us.
